To activate postfix:

- Check the configuration files in /etc/postfix (see ${PREFIX}/share/postfix)
- Modify /etc/mailer.conf (see ${PREFIX}/etc/mailer.conf.postfix)
- Set postfix=YES in /etc/rc.conf
===========================================================================
